Necessary factors:
1. Devlet Bahçeli decides to run for the 2023 presidential election.
2. There is adequate support for Devlet Bahçeli within his political party.
3. General public sentiment favoring Devlet Bahçeli is sufficiently high.
4. None of the other strong potential candidates win a higher share of votes.

1. P(Devlet Bahçeli decides to run for the 2023 presidential election)=0.6
2. P(There is adequate support for Devlet Bahçeli within his political party|Devlet Bahçeli decides to run for the 2023 presidential election)=0.8
3. P(General public sentiment favoring Devlet Bahçeli is sufficiently high|Devlet Bahçeli decides to run for the 2023 presidential election, There is adequate support for Devlet Bahçeli within his political party)=0.5
4. P(None of the other strong potential candidates win a higher share of votes|General public sentiment favoring Devlet Bahçeli is sufficiently high, Devlet Bahçeli decides to run for the 2023 presidential election, There is adequate support for Devlet Bahçeli within his political party)=0.4
Multiplying out the probabilities: 0.6*0.8*0.5*0.4=0.096.
